Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:358281,360158}Drive in a new foreign car, huh?{NOTE:おニューの外車でドライブか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:360158,363036}I hope it rusts to the core. Hah!{NOTE:あれでグッとさつけたつもりいるんだから。はは～んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:08.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:364120,368916}♪ A pauper on the outside, a princess on the inside. ♪{NOTE:襤褸を着てても心は錦。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:368916,372420}♪ Prettier than any flower. ♪{NOTE:どんな花より綺麗だぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.59,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:381137,382597}Be more careful.{NOTE:君無茶すんなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.68,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:382597,384682}Don't jump out so suddenly next time.{NOTE:XXXながらいきなり飛び出すなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:384682,386267}I need to be more careful?!{NOTE:何よ無茶よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:386267,388561}You have some nerve saying that!{NOTE:そっちこそ心得違いもういいとこじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:32.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:388561,392690}You're out of your mind, driving that big car so fast on a cramped road!{NOTE:こんな狭い陸橋へ渋滞のでっかい外車なんか乗り入れたりしてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.10,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:392690,394108}Heh. I see I don't need to worry.{NOTE:へ。安心したよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.15,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:394108,396152}If you're healthy enough to get mad, you're fine.{NOTE:送るだけの元気があれば大丈夫だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:396152,397654}Wow, how cold.{NOTE:ま。涼しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:41.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:397654,401199}Is that all you have to say after you almost killed a person?{NOTE:裏若いXXX轢き殺そうとしておきながら、そんな挨拶があって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:42.53,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:401199,402533}You're right, I'm sorry.{NOTE:じゃあ、ごめん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.03,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:402533,404035}There. Satisfied now?{NOTE:とこれで気がすんだか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:47.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:404035,407455}As if. My body is priceless until marriage.\NTake me to the hospital.{NOTE:とんでもない。お嫁入り前の大事な体なんですから病院行って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.28,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:407455,408289}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.16,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:408289,409165}Ah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:409165,411209}Better do what the lady says.{NOTE:ま、そう言うことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.83,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:411209,412835}You punk.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:418633,419842}Is that you, Kuma-san!?{NOTE:ま、熊さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:421219,423221}Where have you been?{NOTE:一体どこへ行ってたのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:423221,425807}It's been three years already!{NOTE:三年かも姿を見せないでさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:425807,427475}Let's save that talk for later.{NOTE:その話あとで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:09.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:427475,429477}Just leave this to Kuma-san.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.14,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:432480,435149}Hey, hey, hey, hey!{NOTE:えいえいえいえいえい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.52,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:435149,436526}You, buddy.{NOTE:お若いの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:20.61,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:436526,440613}I don't know where you're from, rich fella, but you're in trouble.{NOTE:どこの成金のドラ息子だか知らねえが、大事なXXXのXXXだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:440613,444951}And how about you take off those fancy sunglasses when somebody's talking to you, huh?{NOTE:目障りなその色眼鏡とってもらうじゃねえか。え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.28,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:444951,446285}"Rich fella"?{NOTE:成金のドラ息子？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:449706,450581}{\i1}Oh wow…!{NOTE:あら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:34.66,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:453918,454669}Tsk.{NOTE:チェ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:458172,459006}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:45.55,Default,Kumagorō,1,1,0,,{TIME:461300,465555}You scum! You just took those shades off a second ago and you're already hitting on Nozomi-chan!{NOTE:このやろ。色眼鏡とったXXは、のぞみちゃんに色目何と付け上がって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.09,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:465555,467098}I won't forgive it.{NOTE:もう勘弁ならねぇ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.59,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:467098,468599}Take this!{NOTE:やろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:471602,472478}Kuma-san!{NOTE:熊さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:473521,475732}Kuma-san, hang in there.{NOTE:熊さんしっかりして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.60,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:475732,477608}I'll leave him under your care.{NOTE:この人の介抱は君に任すよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.65,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:478860,480653}Here's some money for a bicycle repair.{NOTE:これは自転車の修理代。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.65,Default,Funny,0,0,0,,{TIME:481612,482655}See ya.{NOTE:じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:22.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:498254,502258}And then I knocked that pompous bastard down with just one punch!{NOTE:そこでXちゃんはな、その気障のやつをガンと一発醸してやった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.50,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:502258,503509}Awesome!{NOTE:よ、いいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.84,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:503509,504844}What happened next?{NOTE:それからどうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.05,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:504844,507054}That's cool and everything, but Kuma-san.{NOTE:ガンはいいけど、熊さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.72,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:507054,508723}What is it, Pops?{NOTE:何だ親父さん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.60,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:509932,511601}You're not young anymore.{NOTE:あんたも若くない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:35.64,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:511601,515646}Why don't you quit drifting and settle down already? A nice bride would suit you.{NOTE:いい加減ほっつき歩く悩めて身の振り方考えな嫁さんでももらってさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.19,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:517106,518191}Whatcha saying?{NOTE:何言ってんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.40,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:518191,521402}You forgot how old Kumagorō here is known as the "Divorcee Kuma".{NOTE:憚りながらこの熊五郎又の名罰一の熊。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.61,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:521402,524614}I'm a master at finding gold. So what does age matter?{NOTE:金鉱探しの名人よ。年もへったくれもあるもんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.19,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:524614,525198}Eh!{NOTE:え！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:50.07,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:525198,530077}One day I'll find an enormous gold nugget in some mountain! Enormous, I say!{NOTE:そのうちどこか山奥でドカンと一発掘り当てて見てる！ドカンっとな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.37,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:530077,531370}Hey, Uncle!{NOTE:おじちゃん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:51.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:531370,531954}Yeah?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.37,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:531954,533372}What is it, Kazuo?{NOTE:何だ、一夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.91,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:533372,535917}The day after tomorrow is Nozomi's birthday.{NOTE:明後日はのぞみねえちゃんの誕生日なんだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:56.83,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:535917,536834}Right?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.91,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:536834,537919}Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.42,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:537919,539420}Eh? I see.{NOTE:え？そうっか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.96,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:539420,540963}Then I've got a question for you, Pops.{NOTE:それで、おやじさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:540963,542173}How old is Nozomi-chan?{NOTE:のぞみちゃんが何歳か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.21,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:543716,546219}She should be about 17, right?{NOTE:17だっけかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.18,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:546219,549180}She grew up to be very pretty.{NOTE:え？どう綺麗になっちまって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.64,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:549180,551641}I guess even ordinary parents can make great kids!{NOTE:鳶が鷹を生むだってこの事だぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:551641,553810}She doesn't resemble you at all, Pops.{NOTE:親父さんの子には見えね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:18.27,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:554519,558272}Your Uncle will give her a great present the day after tomorrow.{NOTE:あさってはこのおじちゃんが凄いもんプレゼントしてやるからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.44,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:558272,559440}Okay!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.40,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:559440,562401}What will you give her, Dad?{NOTE:ね、父ちゃんは何を出してやるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.90,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:562401,563903}I-I haven't decided yet, uh…{NOTE:それはその、何だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.07,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:563903,565071}Yuki, follow me!{NOTE:ユキ、来い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.15,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:567907,569158}Don't be stupid.{NOTE:馬鹿だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.20,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:569158,571202}You can't ask Dad about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.53,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:571202,572537}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:37.08,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:572537,577083}He let Nozomi go to daytime school even though it meant she couldn't help him anymore.{NOTE:補助のアルバイトを辞めさせてものぞみ姉ちゃんを昼間の学校怒らせてやったんだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.00,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:577083,579001}Dad has to work a lot harder.{NOTE:そのぶんだけかかりが大変なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.54,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:579001,582547}That's why he had to quit smoking and needs to save money.{NOTE:だから父ちゃんあれほど好きなタバコもやめて倹約してるんじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.63,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:582547,583631}Save money?{NOTE:倹約？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:51.22,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:584465,591222}Yeah. Even though he wants to give Nozomi a good present, he can't, because he has no money.{NOTE:だからね、のぞみ姉ちゃんに誕生日の贈り物をしたいのは山々だけどお金がないってことなの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.51,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:591222,592515}That sounds tough.{NOTE:厳しいんだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.55,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:592515,593558}It's super tough.{NOTE:厳しいとも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.10,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:593558,596102}Then I'll save too!{NOTE:じゃ、私も倹約するも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.06,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:596102,597061}Eh!?{NOTE:え？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:02.73,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:598145,602733}You're pretty mature for kids!{NOTE:XXXな。年端もいかない子供の身でありながら大人も及ばんね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:06.15,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:602733,606153}How sweet of you to think of your older sister.{NOTE:姉思いってなんていじらしいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:607321,609490}I'm sure she'll pay you back tenfold—{NOTE:ねえちゃんに尽くしてやったらその十倍…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:14.78,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:609490,614787}No, hundredfold, no, thousandfold for it some day!{NOTE:いや、何千何万倍にいつかきっと姉ちゃんが返してくれるだろうぜ。え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.74,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:614787,615746}Tsk.{NOTE:チェ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.87,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:615746,616873}What are you saying?{NOTE:何言ってんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.08,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:616873,619083}I don't want any such repayment.{NOTE:俺そんなお返しなんか手にしてないぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.16,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:619083,620167}Yeah, yeah!{NOTE:そうだ、そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.71,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:620167,622712}We don't need any compensation!{NOTE:私達手当てにXXだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.21,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:622712,624213}Eh?!{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.38,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:624213,626382}They're so mature.{NOTE:ますますえれぇこいつは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:34.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:631429,634181}I can't believe they're saying that.{NOTE:ちびすけ達までがな事言ってくれるんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:634181,636309}I'm not sure who's the older sister here…{NOTE:これじゃどっちが姉だか分かれはしないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.32,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:653951,655328}What's wrong, Miki-san?{NOTE:どうしたんです、美紀さん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.91,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:656329,657914}Mama! This piano is acting up!{NOTE:ママ！このピアノは可笑しいわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.29,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:659916,661292}It just doesn't sound good!{NOTE:全然調子が出はしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.92,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:663628,666923}Miki. You went to the ward office\Ntoday, didn't you?{NOTE:美紀。お前今日区役所へ行ったそうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.34,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:666923,669342}Oh, Daddy, I'm surprised you know about it.{NOTE:あら、パパよくご存知ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.63,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:669342,672637}I heard you went to see the family register. Why?{NOTE:戸籍謄本もらいに行ったそうだが。どうしてだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.18,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:672637,674180}Huh, you know a lot, don't you, Daddy?{NOTE:え、詳しいじゃない、パパ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.59,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:674180,675598}How did you figure it out?{NOTE:どうして知ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:18.22,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:675598,678225}Miki-san, what did you need your birth certificate for?{NOTE:美紀さん何だって戸籍謄本何か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.39,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:678225,680394}Well, it was like this…{NOTE:それはね、こう言うことなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:26.44,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:681812,686442}{\fad(1500,0)\fs25\bord2.5}Father: Kōda Daijirō\NMother: Kōda Sumiyo\NKōda Miki (eldest daughter)
