Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098070,1100739}Now let's see what Nozomi-san has offered me.{NOTE:それよりのぞみさんのプレゼントこそXX。}
